Initialize the Git LFS extension on your local machine:
git lfs install

Display the current version of Git LFS to verify installation:
git lfs version

Tell Git LFS to manage all files ending in .pkl:
git lfs track "*.pkl"

Stage the attributes file that stores your LFS tracking rules: 
git add .gitattributes

Rewrite commit history to move existing large files into LFS storage:
git lfs migrate import --include="fraud_detector.pkl" --everything

Force push the rewritten history to the remote repository
git push origin master --force